projects.title: Prediction of diabetes
projects.description: Diabetes represents a major public health challenge and Machine learning techniques provide a promising way to predict diabetes risk based on patient characteristics and various biomarkers and in this project we used Pima Indians data and some libraries like Pandas, Numpy, Seaborn, Matplotlib to deal with these problems and we use some Model like Logistic Regression, SVC, Random Forest Classifier, Train and test Data, Confusion matrix the study contributes to the advancement of predictive analytics in diabetes management and prevention 2030.
